Taiwan's major exports to Portugal are computers, electronic
products, leather, telephones, and automobile and bicycle parts;
while Portugal's exports to Taiwan center on traditional crafts,
leather shoes, grape wine, olive oil and pulp.

-- Unless granted an official permit, any person or group is
